# CODEOWNERS - Automatic code review assignments
# See: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Documentation
/docs/                 @your-org/your-team
/docs/**/*.md          @your-org/your-team

# Pipeline definitions
/pipeline/             @your-org/your-team
/pipeline/**/*.yaml    @your-org/your-team

# Core orchestrator (critical)
/src/orchestrator/     @your-org/your-team
/src/core/             @your-org/your-team

# Agents and Advisors
/src/agents/           @your-org/your-team
/src/advisors/         @your-org/your-team

# Release and CI/CD
/.github/              @your-org/your-team
/scripts/              @your-org/your-team

# Configuration files
/config/               @your-org/your-team
/pyproject.toml        @your-org/your-team
/requirements.txt      @your-org/your-team

# Root level important files
/README.md             @your-org/your-team
/LICENSE               @your-org/your-team
/CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md    @your-org/your-team
